## apply_expr -> call_kind option(inlined) option(inlining_state) simple simple_args . MINUSGREATER result_continuation exn_continuation [ RPAREN PIPE KWD_WITH KWD_WHERE KWD_IN KWD_ANDWHERE KWD_AND EOF ]
